{"tid":491052,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今日精選 : 莫雅 「騎師王」@ 4.0","createTime":"2017-12-06T07:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-07T09:07:07.000Z","uid":2333,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"50ce08ae5d48abbcc3f8a8c4cf64d8479acbc15c","tid":491052,"uid":2333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:02:16.000Z","msg":"今日「騎師王」莫雅 係100%馬<br />\n點解咁講呀?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分析:<br />\n其實今日騎師王相對上易賭<br />\n但好多馬迷ON99 咁盲買雷神   8倍打到落去而家6.5倍<br />\n反而莫雅只係郁左少少<br />\n<br />\n雷神呢D大仆街   係自己地頭拎晒D FIT馬  梗係好跑啦<br />\n一出到去世界同頂尖高手拍齊其實只係<strong>湯智傑</strong>之流<br />\n<br />\n好入正題<br />\nR4-無限欣賞 :呢隻馬基本上都入硬Q (唔係隻馬勁，係對手太廢)<br />\nR5-喜菜        : 一般貨色   入到P 拎下分算<br />\nR7-事必獲利:谷草1650專家  有權贏埋<br />\n<br />\n贏兩場已經夠做<br />\n始終莫雅騎功咁出色   中上既馬既發揮=西拉/我頓既150%發揮<br />\n所以 今日莫雅@4.0 絕對買得過"},{"pid":"b2fba7800b36e64705135ffb823790e2015f50d5","tid":491052,"uid":2333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:04:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> MOREMORE"},{"pid":"fb5700fb6e739fed91019ca3332495fd855cc9d0","tid":491052,"uid":2333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:04:25.000Z","msg":"EASY BET , EASY MONEY"},{"pid":"d1db5883263b64a9453063459625cf5999355c66","tid":491052,"uid":131176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:07:01.000Z","msg":"睇錯<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">王騎</span>"},{"pid":"71fffb01bf09201aadfeaea7b6b3aa4c35a83015","tid":491052,"uid":7435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:07:52.000Z","msg":"等你好耐了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有無其他可以跟跟"},{"pid":"126d12cf76f9c1bc1a8f75fa5140075c0edde978","tid":491052,"uid":154756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T07:10:35.000Z","msg":"戶崎<i